Package handlers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DeleteDataHandler
    Handler to manage the routes: - /delete/:schema/:name A request will only be forwarded to this handler if its URL exactly matches this structure.
    GetDataHandler
    Handler to manage the routes: - /delete/:schema/:name A request will only be forwarded to this handler if its URL exactly matches this structure.
    GetTableDetailsHandler
    Handler to manage the routes: - /tables/schema/name A request will only be forwarded to this handler if its URL exactly matches this structure.
    GetTablesHandler
    Handler to manage the routes: - /tables/schemaName - /tables If a schema is not provided, the response contains the list of all tables for all schemas.
    GetTableStructureHandler
    Handler to manage the routes: - /tables/:schema/:name/structure A request will only be forwarded to this handler if its URL exactly matches this structure.
    IndexHandler
    Basic Handler for the "/" route.
    InsertDataHandler
    Handler to manage the routes: - /insert/:schema/:name A request will only be forwarded to this handler if its URL exactly matches this structure.
